When you believe all these beliefs to be true and you don't get worry, anger or doubt, it means you are enlightened.
If you get worries, anger or doubt that means you trust these beliefs for the wrong reasons. (Or you simply not believe them at all)
It means your belief lives in a different world. Not in the world of enlightenment.

0. Any belief is true and false sometimes.

1. EVERYTHING is true in some worlds and false in some other worlds.

2. I have no control over anything

3. Nothing is forever

4. There is no me

5. I need to know why

66. I know exactly what each belief really is. I know when and why it came and where it came from. I know where it goes and I know what it does. I know exactly how to deal with it.
